## Bar Chart (Vertical)

```svg
<!-- Y-axis gridlines -->
<line x1="100" y1="200" x2="1100" y2="200" stroke="var(--grid)" stroke-width="1" />
<line x1="100" y1="325" x2="1100" y2="325" stroke="var(--grid)" stroke-width="1" />
<line x1="100" y1="450" x2="1100" y2="450" stroke="var(--grid)" stroke-width="1" />
<line x1="100" y1="575" x2="1100" y2="575" stroke="var(--grid)" stroke-width="1" />

<!-- Y-axis labels -->
<text x="90" y="205" class="axis-label" text-anchor="end">100%</text>
<text x="90" y="330" class="axis-label" text-anchor="end">75%</text>
<text x="90" y="455" class="axis-label" text-anchor="end">50%</text>
<text x="90" y="580" class="axis-label" text-anchor="end">25%</text>
<text x="90" y="705" class="axis-label" text-anchor="end">0%</text>

<!-- Baseline -->
<line x1="100" y1="700" x2="1100" y2="700" stroke="var(--muted)" stroke-width="1" />

<!-- Bars -->
<!-- Bar 1: 75% height = 375px from baseline -->
<rect x="150" y="325" width="120" height="375" fill="var(--accent)" rx="4" />
<text x="210" y="310" class="value" text-anchor="middle">75%</text>
<text x="210" y="730" class="label" text-anchor="middle">[Category 1]</text>

<!-- Bar 2: 60% -->
<rect x="350" y="400" width="120" height="300" fill="var(--accent)" opacity="0.7" rx="4" />
<text x="410" y="385" class="value" text-anchor="middle">60%</text>
<text x="410" y="730" class="label" text-anchor="middle">[Category 2]</text>

<!-- Bar 3: 45% -->
<rect x="550" y="475" width="120" height="225" fill="var(--accent)" opacity="0.5" rx="4" />
<text x="610" y="460" class="value" text-anchor="middle">45%</text>
<text x="610" y="730" class="label" text-anchor="middle">[Category 3]</text>

<!-- Add more bars as needed -->
```

