## Horizontal Bar Chart

Better when category labels are long:

```svg
<!-- Category labels on the left, bars extending right -->
<text x="200" y="220" class="label" text-anchor="end">[Long Category Name 1]</text>
<rect x="210" y="200" width="600" height="30" fill="var(--accent)" rx="4" />
<text x="820" y="222" class="value">75%</text>

<text x="200" y="280" class="label" text-anchor="end">[Long Category Name 2]</text>
<rect x="210" y="260" width="480" height="30" fill="var(--accent)" opacity="0.7" rx="4" />
<text x="700" y="282" class="value">60%</text>

<text x="200" y="340" class="label" text-anchor="end">[Long Category Name 3]</text>
<rect x="210" y="320" width="360" height="30" fill="var(--accent)" opacity="0.5" rx="4" />
<text x="580" y="342" class="value">45%</text>
```

